sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Local SCADA caller
    participant Proxy as SessionProxy / service proxy
    participant Conn as ServerConnection
    participant Stub as SessionStub / nested stub
    participant Service as SCADA service

    Client->>Proxy: Read / Write / Call / Browse / History / NodeMgmt
    Proxy->>Conn: Protocol request
    Conn->>Stub: Dispatch request
    Stub->>Service: Service call or coroutine await
    Service-->>Stub: Result
    Stub-->>Conn: Protocol response
    Conn-->>Proxy: Response
    Proxy-->>Client: Callback / awaitable / promise completion
